sequenceDiagram
  participant Teacher
  participant Server
  participant MongoDB
  participant Agent
  participant Firewall
  Teacher->>Server: Update whitelist/profile
  Server->>MongoDB: Save entry and bump version
  Agent->>Server: POST /api/agents/heartbeat
  Server-->>Agent: force_sync/version change
  Agent->>Server: GET /api/whitelist/agent-sync
  Server-->>Agent: scoped whitelist
  Agent->>Agent: Resolve domains to IPs
  Agent->>Firewall: Update allow rules
